item.title: US-26 West at OR-126 - Prineville
item.description: US-26 West at OR-126 in Prineville. Turn right for US-26 west to Madras and Portland; turn left for OR-126 west to Redmond and Bend.

item.title: End OR-380 West at US-26
item.description: End OR-380 West at US-26 in Prineville. Use US-26 east for Mitchell and John Day; US-26 west for Prineville and Redmond (via OR-126).

item.title: End OR-19 South at US-26
item.description: End OR-19 South at US-26 in Grant County. Turn right for US-26 West to Mitchell and Prineville (Ochoco Highway); turn left for US-26 East to Dayville and John Day (John Day Highway).

item.description: US-97 South approaching OR-126 East (Evergreen Ave.) Use OR-126 east for Prineville and John Day.

item.title: OR-126 East at US-97
item.description: OR-126 East approaching US-97 in Redmond. At the time this photo was taken, US-97 ran through downtown Redmond on two parallel one-way streets. Recently, US-97 passes through Redmond on a bypass.
